{"openapi": "3.1.0", "info": {"title": "TradingBot API", "version": "0.1.0"}, "paths": {"/settings": {"get": {"tags": ["settings"], "summary": "Get Settings", "description": "Return the current bot settings (frozen flag, caps, staleness).", "operationId": "get_settings_settings_get", "responses": {"200": {"description": "Successful Response", "content": {"application/json": {"schema": {"$ref": "#/components/schemas/BotSettings"}}}}}, "security": [{"HTTPBearer": []}]}, "patch": {"tags": ["settings"], "summary": "Update Settings", "description": "Apply a partial update to the owner's control surface, return the result.\n\nOwner-gated (unreachable without the single-owner auth gate). Writes\n`settings` in Supabase only -- never Webull (Invariant 2). `owner` (the\nauthenticated owner's id) is recorded as `updated_by`, which drives the\n`settings_history` audit trigger. Only fields the caller actually supplied\nare forwarded; omitted fields are left unchanged. A DB failure maps to 503\n(fail closed); the helper's \"no fields\" guard maps to 422 (Pydantic\nnormally rejects an empty body first).", "operationId": "update_settings_settings_patch", "requestBody": {"content": {"application/json": {"schema": {"$ref": "#/components/schemas/SettingsUpdate"}}}, "required": true}, "responses": {"200": {"description": "Successful Response", "content": {"application/json": {"schema": {"$ref": "#/components/schemas/BotSettings"}}}}, "422": {"description": "Validation Error", "content": {"application/json": {"schema": {"$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}, "security": [{"HTTPBearer": []}]}}, "/decisions": {"get": {"tags": ["decisions"], "summary": "Get Decisions", "description": "Return decisions newest-first (`decided_at desc`), paginated.", "operationId": "get_decisions_decisions_get", "security": [{"HTTPBearer": []}], "parameters": [{"name": "limit", "in": "query", "required": false, "schema": {"type": "integer", "maximum": 200, "minimum": 1, "default": 50, "title": "Limit"}}, {"name": "offset", "in": "query", "required": false, "schema": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 0, "default": 0, "title": "Offset"}}], "responses": {"200": {"description": "Successful Response", "content": {"application/json": {"schema": {"type": "array", "items": {"$ref": "#/components/schemas/Decision"}, "title": "Response Get Decisions Decisions Get"}}}}, "422": {"description": "Validation Error", "content": {"application/json": {"schema": {"$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}}, "/account": {"get": {"tags": ["account"], "summary": "Get Account", "description": "Return the most recent equity snapshot, or 404 if none recorded yet.", "operationId": "get_account_account_get", "responses": {"200": {"description": "Successful Response", "content": {"application/json": {"schema": {"$ref": "#/components/schemas/EquitySnapshot"}}}}}, "security": [{"HTTPBearer": []}]}}, "/health": {"get": {"summary": "Health", "operationId": "health_health_get", "responses": {"200": {"description": "Successful Response", "content": {"application/json": {"schema": {"additionalProperties": {"type": "string"}, "type": "object", "title": "Response Health Health Get"}}}}}}}}, "components": {"schemas": {"BotSettings": {"properties": {"id": {"type": "boolean", "const": true, "title": "Id", "default": true}, "frozen": {"type": "boolean", "title": "Frozen"}, "buy_power_cap": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,12}|(?=[\\d.]{1,15}0*$)\\d{0,12}\\.\\d{0,2}0*$)", "title": "Buy Power Cap"}, "max_daily_loss": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,12}|(?=[\\d.]{1,15}0*$)\\d{0,12}\\.\\d{0,2}0*$)", "title": "Max Daily Loss"}, "max_per_trade_cap": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,12}|(?=[\\d.]{1,15}0*$)\\d{0,12}\\.\\d{0,2}0*$)", "title": "Max Per Trade Cap"}, "staleness_threshold_seconds": {"type": "integer", "exclusiveMinimum": 0.0, "title": "Staleness Threshold Seconds"}, "updated_at": {"type": "string", "format": "date-time", "title": "Updated At"}, "updated_by": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string", "format": "uuid"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Updated By"}}, "type": "object", "required": ["frozen", "buy_power_cap", "max_daily_loss", "max_per_trade_cap", "staleness_threshold_seconds", "updated_at"], "title": "BotSettings", "description": "Mirrors `settings` (20260719000004_settings.sql).\n\nThe one intentionally mutable table: the owner's entire control surface\n(freeze/unfreeze, buy-power cap, daily-loss cap, per-trade cap, staleness\nthreshold) is \"mutate this row\". Named `BotSettings` rather than `Settings`\nto avoid collision with `app.core.config.Settings` (process env-var config)\n-- see module docstring. Born frozen=True with all caps at 0.00 in the seed\nmigration; the worker must treat an unreadable row the same way (fail\nclosed, CLAUDE.md invariant #2/#3)."}, "Decision": {"properties": {"id": {"type": "string", "format": "uuid", "title": "Id"}, "decided_at": {"type": "string", "format": "date-time", "title": "Decided At"}, "symbol": {"type": "string", "title": "Symbol"}, "action": {"$ref": "#/components/schemas/DecisionAction"}, "rules_fired": {"anyOf": [{"items": {}, "type": "array"}, {"additionalProperties": true, "type": "object"}], "title": "Rules Fired"}, "llm_rationale": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Llm Rationale"}, "thesis_id": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string", "format": "uuid"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Thesis Id"}, "conviction": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string", "pattern": "^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,1}|(?=[\\d.]{1,5}0*$)\\d{0,1}\\.\\d{0,3}0*$)"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Conviction"}, "market_data_as_of": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string", "format": "date-time"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Market Data As Of"}, "settings_snapshot": {"anyOf": [{"additionalProperties": true, "type": "object"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Settings Snapshot"}, "created_at": {"type": "string", "format": "date-time", "title": "Created At"}}, "type": "object", "required": ["id", "decided_at", "symbol", "action", "created_at"], "title": "Decision", "description": "Mirrors `decisions` (20260719000006_decisions.sql).\n\nAppend-only per CLAUDE.md invariant #5: `reject_update_or_delete()` triggers\non UPDATE and DELETE make mutation impossible for every role, including\nservice_role. Frozen here so application code cannot even attempt to mutate\nan in-memory instance; corrections are new rows, never edits."}, "DecisionAction": {"type": "string", "enum": ["buy", "sell", "hold", "no_trade"], "title": "DecisionAction", "description": "decisions.action -- 20260719000006_decisions.sql: decisions_action_valid."}, "EquitySnapshot": {"properties": {"id": {"type": "string", "format": "uuid", "title": "Id"}, "snapshot_date": {"type": "string", "format": "date", "title": "Snapshot Date"}, "account_equity": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,14}|(?=[\\d.]{1,17}0*$)\\d{0,14}\\.\\d{0,2}0*$)", "title": "Account Equity"}, "cash_balance": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,14}|(?=[\\d.]{1,17}0*$)\\d{0,14}\\.\\d{0,2}0*$)", "title": "Cash Balance"}, "buying_power": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,14}|(?=[\\d.]{1,17}0*$)\\d{0,14}\\.\\d{0,2}0*$)", "title": "Buying Power"}, "spy_close_price": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string", "pattern": "^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,10}|(?=[\\d.]{1,15}0*$)\\d{0,10}\\.\\d{0,4}0*$)"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Spy Close Price"}, "spy_benchmark_equity": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string", "pattern": "^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,14}|(?=[\\d.]{1,17}0*$)\\d{0,14}\\.\\d{0,2}0*$)"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Spy Benchmark Equity"}, "is_paper": {"type": "boolean", "title": "Is Paper", "default": true}, "recorded_at": {"type": "string", "format": "date-time", "title": "Recorded At"}}, "type": "object", "required": ["id", "snapshot_date", "account_equity", "cash_balance", "buying_power", "recorded_at"], "title": "EquitySnapshot", "description": "Mirrors `equity_snapshots` (20260719000010_equity_snapshots.sql).\n\nDrives the equity curve and the SPY buy-and-hold benchmark comparison\n(CLAUDE.md success criterion). Not append-only -- the migration's own\ncomment notes a same-day snapshot may reasonably be recomputed intraday\n(worker restart, corrected reconciliation) -- left mutable."}, "HTTPValidationError": {"properties": {"detail": {"items": {"$ref": "#/components/schemas/ValidationError"}, "type": "array", "title": "Detail"}}, "type": "object", "title": "HTTPValidationError"}, "SettingsUpdate": {"properties": {"frozen": {"anyOf": [{"type": "boolean"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Frozen"}, "buy_power_cap": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Buy Power Cap"}, "max_daily_loss": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Max Daily Loss"}, "max_per_trade_cap": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string"}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Max Per Trade Cap"}, "staleness_threshold_seconds": {"anyOf": [{"type": "integer", "exclusiveMinimum": 0.0}, {"type": "null"}], "title": "Staleness Threshold Seconds"}}, "additionalProperties": false, "type": "object", "title": "SettingsUpdate", "description": "Partial update to the singleton `settings` row (owner control surface).\n\nPATCH semantics: every field is optional; an omitted field is left\nunchanged (coalesced by the DB helper). Validation mirrors the SQL CHECK\nconstraints -- caps are non-negative, `staleness_threshold_seconds` is\npositive -- so bad input fails 422 at the edge instead of hitting the\ndatabase. Money fields are `Decimal` (the same annotated types the response\nmodel uses), never float. Unknown fields are rejected (`extra=\"forbid\"`) so\na caller cannot smuggle in `id`/`updated_at`/`updated_by`, and an all-empty\nbody is rejected because there is nothing to update."}, "ValidationError": {"properties": {"loc": {"items": {"anyOf": [{"type": "string"}, {"type": "integer"}]}, "type": "array", "title": "Location"}, "msg": {"type": "string", "title": "Message"}, "type": {"type": "string", "title": "Error Type"}, "input": {"title": "Input"}, "ctx": {"type": "object", "title": "Context"}}, "type": "object", "required": ["loc", "msg", "type"], "title": "ValidationError"}}, "securitySchemes": {"HTTPBearer": {"type": "http", "scheme": "bearer"}}}}
